commit.message:
Add Kraken ledger CSV import (#6)

- Parse Kraken stocks/ETFs/crypto ledger CSV format
- Convert trade and spend/receive pairs into FIFO entries
- Support deposits via optional cost basis provider callback
- Handle EUR.HOLD asset name normalization and fee accounting
- Fees increase cost basis on buys, reduce proceeds on sells
- Add 12 tests covering parsing, fee handling, deposits, and full pipeline

Usage:
  var ledger = LedgerCsvParser.ParseCsv(reader);
  var entries = LedgerCsvParser.ToFifoEntries(ledger, "BTC", "EUR",
      depositCostBasisProvider: deposit => lookupPrice(deposit.Time));
  var result = new BalanceCalculator().Calculate(entries);

